    ("How do you conduct a post-incident review for AI security events?", "A post-incident review examines what happened, how it was detected, response effectiveness, root cause, impact assessment, what worked well, what needs improvement, and specific action items. For AI incidents, also evaluate whether the model needs retraining and defense updates."),
    ("What is the difference between AI monitoring and traditional IT monitoring?", "AI monitoring adds ML-specific metrics like data drift, prediction drift, feature importance changes, model fairness metrics, and adversarial input detection on top of traditional IT metrics like uptime, latency, and error rates. Both are necessary for comprehensive AI system health."),
