    ("How do you set up an AI SOC?", "An AI SOC combines traditional security operations with ML-specific monitoring capabilities. It requires analysts trained in both cybersecurity and ML concepts, specialized tools for model monitoring, playbooks for AI-specific incidents, and integration between ML platforms and SIEM systems."),
