    ("How do you preserve evidence during an AI incident?", "Evidence preservation includes capturing model snapshots, logging all inputs and outputs around the incident timeframe, preserving system logs, recording network traffic, maintaining chain of custody documentation, and ensuring evidence is stored in tamper-proof formats for potential legal proceedings."),
